{"tid":2033444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國海軍成功試射雷射武器 摧毀飛行中無人機","createTime":"2020-05-24T15:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T01:56:14.000Z","uid":141060,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"689a6f0af5be709be86e1662520720586751feae","tid":2033444,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:58:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=392007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392007&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=d97d501c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392007&h=e660af3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=392007</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=14&amp;v=xP94wR-wq4g&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D14%26v%3DxP94wR-wq4g%26feature%3Demb_title&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=22925ace\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=14&amp;v=xP94wR-wq4g&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】美國海軍太平洋艦隊表示，近日成功測試一種新型的高功率激光武器，可摧毀無人機和武裝小艇，將有效提升海軍的實戰能力。<br />\n<br />\n美軍軍艦的甲板發出一道激光，其後一架於空中的無人機着火燃燒並墜落。片段是由美國海軍研究所發布，指波特蘭號兩棲運輸艦本月16日在夏威夷珍珠港附近海域，用固態激光技術聲稱成功擊落一架無人機。<br />\n<br />\n今次測試的艦載高功率激光武器系統展示器，由美國海軍研究所開發，軍方未披露更多細節，但國際戰略研究所前年的一份報告，當時預計這個激光武器功率達到150千瓦。相關武器目前處於第二階段測試。<br />\n<br />\n波特蘭號的指揮官表示，海軍艦艇在執行任務時面臨越來越多威脅，包括無人機、武裝小艇及敵方的監視和偵察系統，類似高功率激光的定向能武器技術將有助美軍提升實戰能力。<br />\n<br />\n而透過海上測試將獲得更多有關固態激光武器對抗潛在威脅的信息，認為波特蘭號憑着這項先進功能，為海上戰爭作出新的定義。<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍早於60年代研發激光、電磁等定向能武器，希望將輻射能聚焦在目標上，並將目標摧毀或破壞。而激光武器的運行速度達到光速，相當於洲際彈道導彈飛行速度的五萬倍。<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍2017年也曾於波斯灣進行與今次類似的測試，並成功擊落一架無人機。"},{"pid":"4237fb7385a9672b8e1d9e8ad6c930a5b0198f86","tid":2033444,"uid":20867,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/8/8c/MRX-009_Psyco_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20120828184058\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fgundam%2Fimages%2F8%2F8c%2FMRX-009_Psyco_Gundam.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20120828184058&h=e784f69e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e0767ceacf3660f1e483bd618c5173b1313d83a","tid":2033444,"uid":19970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:25:21.000Z","msg":"Gundam<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc51472bbc93dbba5d9ad58f0cadfcb2ec9c0872","tid":2033444,"uid":322732,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:30:49.000Z","msg":"同法庭講 呢支先係激光炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af69ba0064da92a2465fa31305660b6bd483d57","tid":2033444,"uid":141164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:33:53.000Z","msg":"打撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ae82aeb1c8845493084b3c01999e4d401feac5","tid":2033444,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8859c00407b868bf2a8190216beeae09c718cc35","tid":2033444,"uid":199957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fc51472bbc93dbba5d9ad58f0cadfcb2ec9c0872","tid":2033444,"uid":322732,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:30:49.000Z","msg":"同法庭講 呢支先係激光炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T18:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出走既手足他日有機會做到海軍記得用呢枝野俾班狗體驗下咩叫激光炮"},{"pid":"d37a26ee91c7890de405071076a2cd6a759a78